      <body>Before this change, the test I added failed.

@@@ ruby
  1) Error:
test_with_array_containing_single_name(PolymorphicRoutesTest):
NoMethodError: undefined method `articles_nil_class_url' for #&lt;PolymorphicRoutesTest:0x1045528&gt;
@@@

However, giving an array consists of an object doesn't raise NoMethodError nor any.

@@@ ruby
def test_with_array_containing_single_object
  @article.save
  expects(:article_url).with(@article)
  polymorphic_url([nil, @article]) # argument will be [@article] with former patch #1317
end
@@@

I wish this explain my intention.</body>
