&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;However, giving an array consists of an object doesn't raise
NoMethodError nor any.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;
def test_with_array_containing_single_object
  @article.save
  expects(:article_url).with(@article)
  polymorphic_url([nil, @article]) # argument will be [@article] with former patch #1317
end
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I wish this explain my intention.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
